high_descs: Move to the cabinet above the small black table.
Open the cabinet and pick up the brown bowl from in there.
Bring the bowl to the sink.
Fill up the bowl with water in the sink.
Bring the bowl to the long white table.
Put the bowl on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl filled with water on the long table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the table, turn right and look up to a cabinet directly above the small black table.
Open the left cabinet door and take out the brown bowl from the cabinet.
Turn right and walk towards the sink on your left.
Put the bowl in the sink, fill it with water, and pick it back up.
Turn left and head towards the table with the toaster.
Place the bowl next to the toaster on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the bowl full of water on the table next to the toaster.

high_descs: turn around and walk to the end of the room, and face right at the kitchen cabinets
grab a dirty bowl out of the cabinets above
move to the right a bit to the kitchen sink
place the bowl inside the kitchen sink and fill it with water
turn around and move over to the kitchen counter with the toaster on it
place the bowl of water to the right of the toaster on the counter
anns.task_desc: place a bowl of water on the kitchen counter to the right of the toaster
